name: Nirmalya Ghosh
bio: Nirmalya is from New Delhi, India and came to Seattle to pursue higher education in 2016. He has been a Seattleite ever since. Nirmalya enjoys finding new places to eat and loves hiking during the summer. His favorite park is Green Lake where he likes to hammock and relax.

name: Evan Marshall
bio: Evan is from Miami, Florida and arrived to Seattle in 2018 when his parents found new jobs in the city. He enjoys checking out new vegetarian restaurants and crate digging at his local record store. His favorite places are the Egyptian Movie theater in Capitol Hill and the restaurant Lost on Mars.

name: Zi Wang
bio: Zi is from Edmonton, Canada and came to Seattle in 2020. She enjoys exploring restaurants across the city to indulge her appetite for dim sum and hot pot. She also lkes to go finding nemo at the Seattle Aquarium, stroll along Discovery Park beach, and snap photos at the Washington Park Arboretum.
